OL,3,CWomen in Guernsey call for more
OL,4,Csupport and awareness for dyslexia
OL,6,FA woman who was diagnosed with
OL,7,Fdyslexia aged 33 is trying to empower
OL,8,Fothers with the neurological condition.
OL,10,FVicki Merrien was diagnosed in
OL,11,FFebruary 2024 and says she was not
OL,12,Fsupported through her exams at school.
OL,14,FBut over the last 15 years, Vicki says
OL,15,Fher dyslexia has not been a barrier in
OL,16,Fher career in the finance industry.
