OL,3,CWomen in Guernsey call for more
OL,4,Csupport and awareness for dyslexia
OL,6,FBut Vicki empowers others with
OL,7,Fdyslexia by demonstrating that it
OL,8,Fshould not be a barrier to success, as
OL,9,Fshe is now a manager in finance.
OL,11,FShe says: "I'm not a person who
OL,12,Fdoesn't like being told I can't
OL,13,Fachieve something so having the
OL,14,Fdiagnosis means I can help answer in
OL,15,Fmy own brain, the way I think and
OL,16,Fprocess things so it makes me
OL,17,Funderstand myself better."
